On our channel we create –∞ trailer mashups ‚ñ∑
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and Add Our Own Dialogues To Make A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot ocr genre of the film entirely.

lyrics :
Kon roklega godsplan? 
Yeah I stammer but yahan better rapper kon hai? 
Kon kacha chabara inhe wrong turn jese
Kon ghodi banara jese porn hai, han? 

Call karein mujhe gyaan dere phone pe
Kam daaalo songs, jyada daalo content han
Karma mountains se baje gaaun sheher mein 
Mera reynolds hai bhaari tere fountain pe 

Kon hai ? Who do this like I do? 
Mein Virat, trash talk karein Rayedu
Bas camera pe baat chodein cartoon. 
Hath mein aajaayegi Jo field pe utaar du, 

Kabhi rap kar du kabhi gaa du haan
Tab bhi likhai mein thodi na jagah du
keep a balance , jese laga gyro
Dena chahre lollipop, m na chaantu

Vo drive kare crazy mein dhundra hoon parking --hmmm.. 
Jahan dikhta ni wahan dete marking --hmm--
I be laughing -hmmm- They be barking -hmm-, 
aaun saamne ye kaanpe kese parkinsons 


Nahi C type, phir bhi nahi hai charging kam
2 invoices, par chaar income
Hum pahadi , mat karo Shanti bhang, 
Chaiye doon mein bahar wali gaadi kam , kher


Whos back? 
Mr. Micro d*ck, I mean, my flow sick, 
Mene ni bola ye, I think my hydro did
A Bit high right now, but no glycodin 
Chaiye tha head ek, par vo laai crocin
Ese hunger bhi kesi ese Khaaye jo scene
Daalu kahi bhi show , aye mere bhailog yea
Thode Rawat aaye, Dobhal and aaye Joshi's
Stage pe stuff fenke , saath mein laaye vo sheet

Yea...Han..

Inhe boldena Hi bola
ADHD, Bipolar , 
Dm mein dolte ye
Bolte reply do na
Hath mein hai dhai tola
Chediyon yahan bhai ko na 
Waqt tera kharaab hai
fake teri Daytona

There bro, Yea I said it. 
Dekha screenshot , f*ck! they hate me on reddit 
Its funny kese karrein ye decide whose legit. 

Gehri khaai, kam hai time, samay se pooch
Like a battleground, jo bhi ho sake tu loot
Koi saath hai to sahi, cut the ties jo hai nahi. 
You should know when to cut, jaake Samay se pooch

Who's back? Rhymes scheme king dancing on your Fencing
Heem kleem kitne ghost writers on that team? 
Cream vream karein roll, stuff chalein passing
Please please karein, maange beekh for attention. 
"Me-Me" karein track pe, such obsession
Chee chee, mat cover karo live sessions
Meet me, Mil please , See, then offend me
Show me thoda passion, show me some aggression. 

Who do this like I do? 
Mein Virat, trash talk karein Rayedu
Bas camera pe baat chodein cartoon. 
Hath mein aajaayegi Jo field pe utaar du, 

Kabhi rap kar du kabhi gaa du haan
Tab bhi likhai mein thodi na jagah du
keep a balance , jese laga gyro
Dena chahre lollipop, mein na chaantu
